data.description: Don't miss out on this incredible home in a quiet cut-de-sac surrounded by tons of mature trees. This home has gone through lots of upgrades in the last 36 months including new kitchen cabinets and appliances in late 2021, a large stamped concrete patio with awning, tons of new tile and flooring, new paint throughout, and so much more! It's one you absolutely have to see in person.
